msgstr ""
"Please also refer to the information in the chapters **Data Exchange - I2C "
"Bus** and **Bus Systems - I2C**."

#: ../../usermanual/configuration.rst:1371 81234d05af654a8f8f75713632f1b326
#, fuzzy
